data.text:
PROFESSIONAL SUMMARY:

11 Years of Business Analysis and Design/Development/implementation experience in Business Intelligence (BI), Data Analytics, Data Modelling & Data Visualization Solutions using QlikView, Qlik Sense, Cognos.

BI / Data Analyst and Technical Lead with Various domain exposures in Banking / Finance, Insurance, Health Care, Retail, Automobile

Experience in all the phases of Data warehouse life cycle involving Requirement Analysis, Design, Coding, Testing, and Deployment.

Contributed as individual contributor at Client Location & worked as Onsite/Off - Shore model

Good experience on implementation of BIDW Life-cycle Projects with Agile (Scrum), Waterfall, Iterative methodology

Strong experience with Dimensional Data Modeling and creating Star Schema / Snowflake Schema

Around 4 Years of experience in working with QlikView / Qlik Sense, Qlik Management Console(QMC), Qlik Sense Cloud, Customization of Qlik Sense Dashboard using Java Script, JSON, XML code

Hands on Experience with Qlik Architecture in Design, Development, Deployment and Migration along with Qlik Server and Publisher

Mastery of QlikView / Qlik Sense charting, Set Analysis, Variables, Templates, Incremental Load and building/deploying Section Access.

Strong knowledge on QlikView / Qlik Sense server architecture, building QVDs and QVWs applying business rules and data validations.

Expertise in Creating Dashboards using various QlikView / Qlik Sense Sheet objects and using different data sources like Oracle, SQL Server, QVD files and excel.

Involved in Admin activities like User Access, Deployment & Monitoring of Dashboards

Key Member of BI Practice with participation in various RFPs, architecture reviews, Estimation, Capacity Planning & Staffing requirement of a new project.

Working as Business Analyst (BA) role as requirement gathering, Client-interfacing, creating Technical, Functional and Non-Functional Requirement documents, High Level and Detailed Design Documents, Master Test Plan, User Guides and involved in Change Management (CR) & UAT process.

Extensive exposure in various Cognos platforms.

Good knowledge on overall ETL process & Tableau Development

Conducting Training activities on QlikView, Qlik Sense & Cognos

TECHNICAL SKILLS:

Qlik Tools: QlikView 11x (QlikView Desktop, QlikView Management Console), Qlik Sense 2x / 3x

Tableau Tools: Tableau 10x / 9x (Tableau Desktop & Tableau Server)

IBM Cognos Tools: Cognos 10x / 8x (Report Studio, Framework Manager, Dynamic Cube, Transformer)

Database: Oracle 9i / 11g, SQL Server 2008, Teradata, DB2

Others: ServiceNow, HPQC, Project & Portfolio Management (PPM), JIRA, Toad, SVN, PVCS

PROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE:

Confidential, New Jersey

QlikView / Qlik Sense Development Lead

Environment: QlikView 11.2 SR8, Qlik Sense 3.1, Qlik Management Console, Oracle 11g, SQL Server 2008

Responsibilities:

Responsible for requirement gathering, analysis of the functional specifications, design reports / dashboards & involved in successful deployment.

Facilitating client meetings, project review and working closely with Onsite/Offshore team to ensure successful completion of on-time project deliverables.

Involved in Code review, Unit Testing & mentoring the team on need basis

Maintained Version control using SVN

Key member in set-up multiple environments like DEV, QA, UAT & PROD

Participating & Demo to client for User Acceptance Testing (UAT)

Estimate New Development & Change Request (CR) with Impact Analysis

Designed & Developed 3 tier Data Architecture

Created QVDs & updated on timely basis by using Incremental Load

Developed Linked Tables, Concatenation (Resolving Synthetic Keys, Loops & model ambiguity).

Used various scripting functions to improve the performance

Developed QlikView Dashboards using various Charts with added functionality like Drill Down, Drill up & Cyclic Grouping, Pivot Table, Input Field, Table Box

Developed Qlik Sense Dashboard using Templates, Master Library items and Story Generation

Maintaining the Dashboard in Qlik Sense Cloud

Customization of Qlik Sense Dashboard using Java Script, JSON, XML code

Developed KPIâ€™s, Set Analysis, Variables and implemented triggers/macros to provide custom functionality in Dashboards

Involved in re-designing of Dashboards based upon User feedback

Scheduled & Distributed QVDs and Dashboards in Server level

Involved Admin activities like User Access & Deployment in QMC.

Fully involved in the Release Management process & monitoring for successful deployment

Creating Various Objects in QlikView such as Straight Table, Pivot Table, List box, Statistics box, Multi box, Table box, Charts, Input box, Current Selection box, Button etc...

Using Set Analysis to filter data into business logic.

Security implementation using Section Access in QlikView.

Reload Documents and Deploy Applications through QlikView Management Console in Development for verification.

For Migration purpose, using the existing logic in Cognos & created the Dashboard from scratch in QlikView and Qlik Sense with some added functionality
